


Kabusa neɣ Qulusa qqaren-as diɣ Ɣulusa ; d mmi-s amenzu n [[Ulzasen]] , yenɣa-t gma-s [[Lakumzis]] ardekal tagrawla n [[Meṭzul]] fella-s .

== Tudert ==
Ass mi yemmut baba-s Ulzasen yuɣal d netta i d agellid imi akka i t-id wwin yigeldunen n Masilya . Yexdem fella-s yiwen seg yiɣella itekkan ɣer twaculin tinesbaɣrin yemmezwaǧen d twacult-nsen . Maca Meṭzul neɣ Lakumzis ur sɛin ara azref ad gelden tura ; ilaq ad rǧun armi yuɣal Masensen d agellid yernu ad yemmet , akken ad yegled Lakumzis .

Yekker uredwir gar ugellid d ugrawliw , tfuk tegrawla-agi s lmut n Kabusa .
